author Kubo100x created Wed Jul 15 07:53:51 +0000 2026
text Update on Octra HFHE v2 public audit. |  | Day 6 algebraic track complete: | • reduced-param invariant scan (480 samples, 6 keys, 1104 features): 0 survive FDR | • ciphertext-algebra toy: 0.000000 TVD between distinct plaintexts | • no low-dim simplification lowers the LPN-PRF margin (n=4096, τ=1/8) |  | The wrapper doesn't leak.  | No equality oracle from algebra. |  | research notes only not a formal audit or security proof. |  | Negative result independently reproduced. | No duplicate PRs — smoke-ui already holds INFO-001..005. |  | Contributing the full assessment + reproducible tools to @Hikkimori  |  | open source: | https://github.com/smoke-ui/octra-hfhe-v2-security-assessment |  | Status: DAY6 PASS.  | Next = Day 7 freeze.
