## https://x.com/Kubo100x/status/2075388207882256852
api https://api.fxtwitter.com/Kubo100x/status/2075388207882256852 status 200 bytes 5366
author Kubo100x created Fri Jul 10 01:14:42 +0000 2026
text spent time investigating the Octra HFHE v2 bounty from the public artifacts. |  | Looked at: | • fused ciphertext structure | • N0/N1 field relations | • Pedersen commitment behavior | • PRF + multi-block patterns | • sparse H properties | • repo history |  | no practical public recovery path found so far. | v2 appears to have removed the v1 R_com oracle weakness. |  | research notes only | not a formal audit or security proof. |  | thanks Hermes + Grok 4.5
